ZH: 他没有告发那个罪犯。
EN: He did not report the criminal.

ZH: 我决定告发这个不义的行为。
EN: I have decided to denounce this unjust behavior.

ZH: 她勇敢地告发了她的施虐者。
EN: She bravely reported her abuser.

ZH: 我不敢告发他，因为我害怕报复。
EN: I dare not report him because I am afraid of retaliation.

ZH: 他因为涉嫌受贿而被告发。
EN: He was reported for suspected bribery.

ZH: 如果你发现任何不正常行为，请告发。
EN: If you notice any abnormal behavior, please report it.

ZH: 他是个告发者，不是间谍。
EN: He is an informant, not a spy.

ZH: 这位警察要求所有目击者告发任何线索。
EN: The police officer requested all witnesses to report any leads.

ZH: 她想尽一切办法来告发那个犯罪团伙。
EN: She tried every means to denounce the criminal gang.

ZH: 这个组织鼓励人们勇于告发腐败现象。
EN: This organization encourages people to courageously expose corruption.

ZH: 他勇敢地告发了公司内部的不法行为。
EN: He courageously reported the illicit behavior within the company.

ZH: 我不会保持沉默，我会告发这个不公正的制度。
EN: I will not remain silent; I will report this unjust system.

ZH: 我希望有更多人能勇于告发不公正对待。
EN: I hope more people will have the courage to report unfair treatment.

ZH: 她被迫告发了她的同事，因为她知道他们是内鬼。
EN: She was forced to denounce her colleagues because she knew they were moles.

ZH: 他告发了那个盗窃团伙，希望能为社会做出贡献。
EN: He reported the theft gang, hoping to make a contribution to society.

ZH: 政府鼓励公民告发任何有关恐怖主义的线索。
EN: The government encourages citizens to report any leads regarding terrorism.

ZH: 这个组织的目标是告发贪污和腐败。
EN: The organization's objective is to expose embezzlement and corruption.

ZH: 警方将保护任何人告发犯罪行为的安全。
EN: The police will ensure the safety of anyone reporting criminal activities.

ZH: 她被迫告发了她的上司，因为他涉嫌贪污。
EN: She was compelled to report her boss because he was suspected of embezzlement.

ZH: 勇敢的人总是敢于告发不公正的行为。
EN: Brave individuals are always willing to denounce unjust actions.

ZH: 学校鼓励学生告发欺凌行为，以维护校园安全。
EN: The school encourages students to report bullying incidents to maintain campus safety.
